{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-11",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_11_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 11 - Gutman",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 2,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 241.74,
  "page_end_sec": 483.62,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.658,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 241.74,
      "end": 243.34,
      "text": "He took his arm from around her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.46,
      "end": 244.78,
      "text": "took a card from his pocket,"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.18,
      "end": 246.72,
      "text": "scribbled three lines on its back,"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.78,
      "end": 247.56,
      "text": "and gave it to her."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.2,
      "end": 250.9,
      "text": "\"'You can tell Sid everything,' he frowned."
    },
    {
      "start": 251.42,
      "end": 252.2,
      "text": "\"'Or almost everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.84,
      "end": 255.04,
      "text": "Where were you the night Miles was shot?"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.34,
      "end": 256.72,
      "text": "At home,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 256.86,
      "end": 258.7,
      "text": "she replied without hesitation."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.06,
      "end": 260.8,
      "text": "He shook his head,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 260.9,
      "end": 261.58,
      "text": "grinning at her."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.16,
      "end": 262.82,
      "text": "I was,"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.16,
      "end": 264.1,
      "text": "she insisted."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.92,
      "end": 265.2,
      "text": "No,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 265.48,
      "end": 266.12,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.72,
      "end": 267.65,
      "text": "but if that's your story,"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.88,
      "end": 268.9,
      "text": "it's all right with me."
    },
    {
      "start": 269.52,
      "end": 270.44,
      "text": "Go see Sid."
    },
    {
      "start": 271.136,
      "end": 272.08,
      "text": "It's up at the next corner,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 272.24,
      "end": 272.98,
      "text": "the pinkish building,"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.2,
      "end": 273.83,
      "text": "room 827."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.01,
      "end": 277.96,
      "text": "Her blue eyes tried to probe his yellow-gray ones.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 279.5,
      "end": 281.02,
      "text": "What makes you think I wasn't home?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 281.22,
      "end": 282.48,
      "text": "She asked slowly."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.3,
      "end": 283.94,
      "text": "Nothing,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 284.1,
      "end": 285.56,
      "text": "except I know you weren't."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.44,
      "end": 287.02,
      "text": "But I was!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 287.3,
      "end": 287.8,
      "text": "I was!"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.04,
      "end": 289.74,
      "text": "She bit her lip.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 290.688,
      "end": 291.88,
      "text": "Anger darkened her eyes.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 293.376,
      "end": 294.18,
      "text": "Effie told you that?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 294.98,
      "end": 296.04,
      "text": "She said indignantly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 297.0,
      "end": 299.48,
      "text": "I saw her looking at my clothes and snooping around.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 300.42,
      "end": 301.58,
      "text": "You know she doesn't like me,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 301.66,
      "end": 301.84,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.64,
      "end": 304.6,
      "text": "Why do you believe things she tells you when you",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 304.6,
      "end": 306.82,
      "text": "know she'd do anything to make trouble for me?"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.24,
      "end": 308.38,
      "text": "Mm,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 308.54,
      "end": 309.24,
      "text": "you women,"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.44,
      "end": 311.0,
      "text": "Spade said gently."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.74,
      "end": 313.6,
      "text": "He looked at the watch on his wrist.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 314.62,
      "end": 315.48,
      "text": "\"'You'll have to trot along,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 315.64,
      "end": 315.9,
      "text": "precious."
    },
    {
      "start": 316.34,
      "end": 317.72,
      "text": "I'm late for an appointment now."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.54,
      "end": 319.3,
      "text": "You do what you want,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 319.42,
      "end": 320.5,
      "text": "but if I were you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.68,
      "end": 322.72,
      "text": "I'd tell Sid the truth or nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.15,
      "end": 323.98,
      "text": "I mean,"
    },
    {
      "start": 323.98,
      "end": 326.1,
      "text": "leave out the parts you don't want to tell him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.42,
      "end": 328.43,
      "text": "but don't make up anything to take its place.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 329.82,
      "end": 330.7,
      "text": "\"'I'm not lying to you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 330.76,
      "end": 332.62,
      "text": "Sam,' she protested."
    },
    {
      "start": 333.856,
      "end": 335.48,
      "text": "\"'Like hell you're not,' he said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 335.64,
      "end": 336.32,
      "text": "and stood up."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.46,
      "end": 339.92,
      "text": "She strained on tiptoe to hold her face near his.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 341.5,
      "end": 343.82,
      "text": "\"'You don't believe me?' she whispered.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 344.8,
      "end": 345.96,
      "text": "\"'I don't believe you.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 347.136,
      "end": 348.2,
      "text": "\"'And you won't forgive me",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 349.1,
      "end": 350.02,
      "text": "for—for what I did?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 350.848,
      "end": 351.68,
      "text": "\"'Sure I do.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 352.1,
      "end": 354.0,
      "text": "He bent his head and kissed her mouth."
    },
    {
      "start": 355.008,
      "end": 355.54,
      "text": "\"'That's all right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 355.7,
      "end": 356.992,
      "text": "Now run along.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.98,
      "end": 359.16,
      "text": "She put her arms around him.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 360.16,
      "end": 361.4,
      "text": "\"'Won't you go with me to see Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 361.56,
      "end": 362.01,
      "text": "Wise?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.92,
      "end": 363.52,
      "text": "\"'I can't,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 363.52,
      "end": 365.0,
      "text": "and I'd only be in the way.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 366.12,
      "end": 367.04,
      "text": "He patted her arms,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 367.18,
      "end": 368.52,
      "text": "took them from around his body,"
    },
    {
      "start": 368.62,
      "end": 370.88,
      "text": "and kissed her left wrist between glove and sleeve."
    },
    {
      "start": 371.6,
      "end": 373.54,
      "text": "He put his hands on her shoulders,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 373.84,
      "end": 375.28,
      "text": "turned her to face the door,"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.42,
      "end": 375.88,
      "text": "and"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.98,
      "end": 377.2,
      "text": "released her with a little push."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.56,
      "end": 378.84,
      "text": "Beat it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 378.98,
      "end": 379.72,
      "text": "he ordered."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.13,
      "end": 387.02,
      "text": "The mahogany door of Suite 12C at the Alexandria Hotel was opened by",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 387.02,
      "end": 389.5,
      "text": "the boy Spade had talked to in the Belvedere lobby."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.752,
      "end": 391.22,
      "text": "Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 391.74,
      "end": 392.26,
      "text": "Hello."
    },
    {
      "start": 393.06,
      "end": 393.76,
      "text": "Good-naturedly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 394.22,
      "end": 395.82,
      "text": "The boy did not say anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 396.4,
      "end": 398.58,
      "text": "He stood aside holding the door open."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.52,
      "end": 400.2,
      "text": "Spade went in.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 400.36,
      "end": 400.46,
      "text": "him."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.78,
      "end": 402.46,
      "text": "A fat man came to meet him."
    },
    {
      "start": 403.08,
      "end": 405.42,
      "text": "The fat man was flabbily fat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.62,
      "end": 407.08,
      "text": "with bulbous pink cheeks"
    },
    {
      "start": 407.08,
      "end": 408.76,
      "text": "and lips and chins and neck,"
    },
    {
      "start": 408.88,
      "end": 411.98,
      "text": "with a great soft egg of a body that was all his torso,"
    },
    {
      "start": 412.68,
      "end": 414.74,
      "text": "and pendant cones for arms and legs.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 416.38,
      "end": 419.36,
      "text": "As he advanced to meet Spade all his bulbs rose",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 419.62,
      "end": 421.88,
      "text": "and shook and fell separately with each step,"
    },
    {
      "start": 422.0,
      "end": 424.72,
      "text": "in the manner of clustered soap-bubbles not"
    },
    {
      "start": 424.86,
      "end": 426.96,
      "text": "yet released from the pipe through which they had been blown."
    },
    {
      "start": 428.16,
      "end": 428.62,
      "text": "His eyes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 428.8,
      "end": 429.92,
      "text": "made small by fat"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.08,
      "end": 430.88,
      "text": "puffs around them,"
    },
    {
      "start": 431.04,
      "end": 432.28,
      "text": "were dark and sleek."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.376,
      "end": 435.56,
      "text": "Dark ringlets thinly covered his broad scalp.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 436.28,
      "end": 436.38,
      "text": "He",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 437.18,
      "end": 438.32,
      "text": "wore a black cutaway coat,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 438.58,
      "end": 439.4,
      "text": "black vest,"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.72,
      "end": 442.6,
      "text": "black satin ascot tie holding a pinkish pearl,"
    },
    {
      "start": 442.92,
      "end": 443.42,
      "text": "striped"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.46,
      "end": 445.7,
      "text": "gray worsted trousers and patent-leather shoes."
    },
    {
      "start": 446.624,
      "end": 448.96,
      "text": "His voice was a throaty purr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 449.14,
      "end": 449.248,
      "text": "\"'Ah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.18,
      "end": 450.5,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 450.68,
      "end": 452.92,
      "text": "Spade,' he said with enthusiasm,"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.2,
      "end": 455.76,
      "text": "and he held out a hand like a fat pink star."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.992,
      "end": 458.46,
      "text": "Spade shook the hand and smiled,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 458.64,
      "end": 459.44,
      "text": "but said nothing."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.64,
      "end": 462.48,
      "text": "Spade sat in a soft green chair.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 463.38,
      "end": 466.4,
      "text": "The fat man began to fill two glasses from bottle and siphon.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 467.24,
      "end": 467.98,
      "text": "The boy disappeared.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 469.248,
      "end": 471.62,
      "text": "Doors set in three of the room's walls were closed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 472.4,
      "end": 473.04,
      "text": "The fourth wall,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 473.2,
      "end": 474.18,
      "text": "behind Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.3,
      "end": 476.98,
      "text": "was pierced by two windows looking out over Geary Street."
    },
    {
      "start": 478.5,
      "end": 479.38,
      "text": "\"'We begin well,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 479.46,
      "end": 481.44,
      "text": "sir,' the fat man purred,"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.56,
      "end": 482.68,
      "text": "turning with a proffered"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.68,
      "end": 483.62,
      "text": "glass in his hand."
    }
  ]
}